OL,3,CWelsh farmer says proposed grant shake-
OL,4,Cup will 'cost our children's future'
OL,6,FA new subsidy scheme for Welsh farmers
OL,7,Fis going to "cost us and our
OL,8,Fchildren's future", say those in the
OL,9,Fsector as tensions escalate.
OL,11,FFirst Minister Mark Drakeford says the
OL,12,FWelsh Government is "working with
OL,13,Ffarmers" and that reforms are
OL,14,F"unavoidable".
OL,16,FUK and Welsh Governments are
OL,17,Fintroducing they used to receive when
OL,18,FBritain was part of the European Union.
