OL,3,CWelsh farmer says proposed grant shake-
OL,4,Cup will 'cost our children's future'
OL,6,FThe systems in Wales and in England
OL,7,Fare aimed at switching the grants paid
OL,8,Fto farmers and landowners to rewards
OL,9,Ffor looking after and improving the
OL,10,Fenvironment.
OL,12,FBut Celia Williams, who runs Abbey
OL,13,FFarm Rhuddlan, says it would be a big
OL,14,Fblow for their business. She estimates
OL,15,Fthey would lose 35 acres and have
OL,16,Ffewer cows, sheep and lambs.
OL,18,FShe told ITV Wales: "For years and
OL,19,Fyears we've been put on, put on, put
OL,20,Fon. We've got children that we want to
OL,21,Fhave a future farm for.
