OL,3,CWelsh farmer says proposed grant shake-
OL,4,Cup will 'cost our children's future'
OL,6,F"We're here to support their (Welsh
OL,7,FGovernment) targets, but you can't do
OL,8,Fit at a cost to us".
OL,10,FMs Williams added: "We all want to do
OL,11,Four best for the environment and we do
OL,12,Fthrough the current schemes but these
OL,13,Ffuture schemes just aren't sustainable.
OL,15,F"We all want to do our bit but it's
OL,16,Fjust not sustainable, it's going to be
OL,17,Fat a cost to farmers and a cost to our
OL,18,Fchildren's future."
