OL,3,CWelsh farmer says proposed grant shake-
OL,4,Cup will 'cost our children's future'
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government plans require
OL,7,Ffarmers and landowners to devote 10%
OL,8,Fof their land to tree planting to
OL,9,Fqualify for the payouts, with another
OL,10,F10% planned for wildlife habitat.
OL,12,FBryn Davies, a dairy farmer in Mostyn,
OL,13,FFlintshire, says he can understand the
OL,14,Fneed to address climate change but
OL,15,Fsays the proposals are going to come
OL,16,Fat too great a cost to the farming
OL,17,Fsector.
