OL,3,CWelsh farmer says proposed grant shake-
OL,4,Cup will 'cost our children's future'
OL,6,FHe said: "All of us farmers in Wales
OL,7,Fare annoyed, how would you like it if
OL,8,Fsomeone came into your garden to take
OL,9,F10% of it?"
OL,11,FMr Davies also has concerns about the
OL,12,Ftree-planting element of the scheme
OL,13,Fsaying, "there'll be more badgers,
OL,14,Fmore bovine TB".
OL,16,FDairy farmer Ewan Davies, from Elwy
OL,17,FValley, said he has lost 30 cows to
OL,18,Ftuberculosis since September. He said
OL,19,Fhe "won't take up" the sustainable
OL,20,Ffarming scheme, adding "that's it, end
OL,21,Fof story".
