OL,6,FMali said: "It's important that
OL,7,Feveryone understands that our futures
OL,8,Fare getting ruined."
OL,10,FElla says "the public is supportive"
OL,11,Fof those working in the farming
OL,12,Fsector, adding: "Without us, what are
OL,13,Fyou going to do?"
OL,15,FShe said: "It's not just us that's the
OL,16,Fproblem with the climate. We're doing
OL,17,Fit (farming) so everyone can have
OL,18,Ffood."
