OL,6,FThe Welsh Government's farming subsidy
OL,7,Fscheme is currently out for
OL,8,Fconsultation and thousands of farmers
OL,9,Fhave attended the roadshow sessions
OL,10,Facross Wales.
OL,12,FFirst Minister Mark Drakeford says
OL,13,Fthat reforms are "unavoidable".
OL,15,FThe First Minister told ITV Wales:
OL,16,F"We've changed and adapted the
OL,17,Fproposals having heard the views and
OL,18,Fadvice of farmers, and I'm quite sure
OL,19,Fthey will change again in future.
