OL,3,CWelsh farmer says proposed grant shake-
OL,4,Cup will 'cost our children's future'
OL,6,F"No farmer has to sign up, it's
OL,7,Fvoluntary, around half the farms in
OL,8,FWales aren't signed up to the current
OL,9,Fscheme.
OL,11,F"I understand farmers do feel under
OL,12,Fpressure, including the real tragedy
OL,13,Fof TB in cattle, I understand the way
OL,14,Fthey feel about the future.
OL,16,F"Our aim is to bring farmers with us,
OL,17,Fbut there is a bargain. We want to
OL,18,Finvest in their futures, but the Welsh
OL,19,Fpublic that is providing that
OL,20,Finvestment is entitled to a return on
OL,21,Fthat investment.
